.TH YAD 1 "March 24, 2023"  "yad GTK+ 2.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
yad \- display GTK+ dialogs from shell scripts or command-line

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B yad
.RI [ OPTIONS ]

.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBYAD\fP displays GTK+ dialogs, and returns the user's input
through the program exit code and on standard output.
.PP
\fBYAD\fP is a fork of the \fBZenity\fP program.
.PP
This manual page is about the GTK+-2 and GTK+-3 version maintained independently from
the original YAD project. See the \fIMAINTAINERS\fP section for more.

.SH OPTIONS
This program follows the usual GNU command line syntax, with long
options starting with two dashes (\-\-).

