.B \-\-align=\fITYPE\fP
Set alignment of bar labels. \fITYPE\fP can be \fIleft\fP, \fIcenter\fP or \fIright\fP.
.TP
.B \-\-auto-close
Close the dialog when all bars (or only the watched bar) reach 100%.
